feat(consensus): quadratic proposer selection (#1)

Implement quadratic proposer selection using sqrt(votingPower) normalized to totalVotingPower scale to promote more equitable block production distribution.

- Proposer priority increments by normalized sqrt(votingPower) instead of linear
- Maintains all security invariants and Byzantine fault tolerance
- Based on mathematical principle: cost = votes^2 for diminishing returns


